snippet.title: v6.6 Woven from Last Snow Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd is ascending to v6.6 Woven from Last Snow!
New S-rank battlesuit Misteln Schariac Dreamweaver and SP battlesuit PROMETHEUS Terminal Aide 0017 debut!
Story Chapter XXXVII and featured event TeRiRi's Magical Quest to be released! Stay tuned!

Voice Artists:
Misteln Schariac: Kobayashi Yū
Prometheus: Kana Asumi
Vita: Yoko Hikasa
Sage of the High Tower: Mai Nakahara
